OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA bright end
OL,6,Fto the afternoon with a few isolated
OL,7,Fshowers lingering into the evening,
OL,8,Fhowever most places becoming dry
OL,9,Fovernight with cloudier skies
OL,10,Fdeveloping after midnight. Turning
OL,11,Fchilly in places with a touch of rural
OL,12,Ffrost. Winds easing.
OL,13,
OL,14,CFriday:FA largely cloudy morning on
OL,15,FFriday but bright or sunny spells
OL,16,Fdeveloping at times. Cloudier by late
OL,17,Fafternoon with some patchy rain.
OL,18,FBreeze picking up.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
